# 📊 Data Science Lab (R)

This folder contains the laboratory programs and practical assignments completed as part of the **Data Science Lab** course using **R Programming**.

## 📂 Contents

- Data Import & Export
- Data Cleaning
- Data Manipulation
- Data Visualization
- Statistical Analysis
- Basic Machine Learning
- Lab Assignments

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- R
- RStudio

## 🎯 Objective

To develop practical skills in data analysis, visualization, and statistical computing using R Programming.
